Field.Name: Local Datum
Field.Description: defined in IHO Publication S-60, Appendices B and C. First three chars are datum ID as per IHO tables. Fourth char is local datum subdivision code.

Field.Name: Reference Datum
Field.Description: defined in IHO Publication S-60, Appendices B and C. First three chars are datum ID as per IHO tables. Fourth char is local datum subdivision code.

Field.Name: Delta X
Field.Description: Delta shift in X axis from WGS 84

Field.Name: Delta Y
Field.Description: Delta shift in Y axis from WGS 84

Field.Name: Delta Z
Field.Description: Delta shift in Z axis from WGS 84

Field.Name: Rotation in X
Field.Description: Rotational shift in X axis from WGS 84. Rotations presented use the geodetic sign convention. When looking along the positive axis towards the origin, counter-clockwise rotations are positive.

Field.Name: Rotation in Y
Field.Description: Rotational shift in Y axis from WGS 84. Rotations presented use the geodetic sign convention. When looking along the positive axis towards the origin, counter-clockwise rotations are positive.

Field.Name: Rotation in Z
Field.Description: Rotational shift in Z axis from WGS 84. Rotations presented use the geodetic sign convention. When looking along the positive axis towards the origin, counter-clockwise rotations are positive.

Field.Name: Ellipsoid Semi-major Axis
Field.Description: Semi-major axis (a) of the User Datum ellipsoid

Field.Name: Ellipsoid Flattening Inverse
Field.Description: Flattening (1/f) of the User Datum ellipsoid

Field.Name: Datum Name
Field.Description: 4 character code from IHO Publication S-60,Appendices B and C. First three chars are datum ID as per IHO tables. Fourth char is local datum subdivision code.
